name: element/dusk colorimeter
description: Since 2018, we've trained GANs as part of the Potential Herbarium series, on more than 4 million herbarium boards, and generated many fascinating imaginary plant shapes. These shapes are quite anti-darwinian, and are a seminal constituant of our visual research at @aurecevettier.  Among the signals generated from herbarium, distorted colorimeters are probably the most startling. JPG 3456 × 2592 Ref. AV-2021-U-108
